'''莎拉·吉爾伯特'''（{{lang-en|Sara Gilbert}}，{{bd|1975年|1月29日|catIdx=G}}），美國演員，以1988年至1997年期間在[[情境喜劇|情境喜劇]]《[[羅斯安家庭生活|羅斯安家庭生活]]》中飾演達蓮娜·康納-希利（{{lang|en|Darlene Conner-Healy}}）一角著稱。

==个人生活==
2010年吉爾伯特[[出柜|出柜]]承认自己是[[女同性恋|女同性恋]]。<ref>{{cite news | url=http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/07/30/roseannes-sara-gilbert-confirms-shes-a-lesbian/ | work=CNN | title='Roseanne's' Sara Gilbert confirms she's a lesbian | date=2010-07-30 | accessdate=2012-09-21 | archive-date=2018-12-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181225013318/http://marquee.blogs.cnn.com/2010/07/30/roseannes-sara-gilbert-confirms-shes-a-lesbian/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>2001年，她开始了与电视制片人[[艾利森·艾德勒|艾利森·艾德勒]]（Allison Adler）的恋情。她们有两个孩子：1个儿子Levi Hank，出生于2004年10月，生母是艾德勒<ref name=People>Peiffer, Kim. [http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20010589,00.html "Roseanne's Sara Gilbert Expecting Second Child"]. ''[[People_(magazine)|People]]''. February 2, 2007. Retrieved July 31, 2007.</ref>；1个女儿Sawyer，出生于2007年8月2日，生母是吉爾伯特。<ref name=Celebrity_Babies>[http://www.celebrity-babies.com/2007/08/sara-gilbert-an.html "Sara Gilbert and partner welcome second child"]. Retrieved 2007-08-06.</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,293089,00.html|title=Sara Gilbert Gives Birth to Baby Girl|accessdate=2009-11-08|work=Fox News|date=2007-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090208205953/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,293089,00.html|archive-date=2009-02-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>吉爾伯特和艾德勒在2011年8月分手。<ref>Jordan, Julie. [http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20522469,00.html "The Talk's Sara Gilbert, Partner Break Up"]. ''People''. August 24, 2011. Retrieved August 25, 2011.</ref>分手后吉爾伯特开始与音乐人[[Linda_Perry|Linda Perry]]交往。<ref>Grossberg, Josh [http://www.eonline.com/news/sara_gilbert_talks_relationship_with/277646 "Sara Gilbert Talks Relationship With Linda Perry on The Talk"]. ''E Online''. November 30, 2011. Retrieved December 1, 2011.</ref>吉尔伯特于2013年4月宣布她们订婚<ref>{{cite web|last=Rice |first=Lynette |url=http://insidetv.ew.com/2013/04/08/sara-gilbert-announces-engagement-on-the-talk/l |title=Sara Gilbert announces engagement on 'The Talk' |publisher=Entertainment Weekly |date=2013-04-08 |accessdate=2013-04-09}}</ref>并于2014年3月30日结婚。<ref>{{cite web|last=Lee|first=Esther|title=Sara Gilbert and Linda Perry Are Married|url=http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/sara-gilbert-and-linda-perry-are-married-2014313|publisher=US Weekly|accessdate=2014-03-31|date=2014-03-31|archive-date=2017-07-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170706095501/http://www.usmagazine.com/celebrity-news/news/sara-gilbert-and-linda-perry-are-married-2014313|dead-url=no}}</ref>吉尔伯特在2015年2月28日生下了她们的儿子Rhodes Emilio Gilbert Perry。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://celebritybabies.people.com/2015/03/02/sara-gilbert-linda-perry-welcome-son-rhodes-emilio/ | title=Sara Gilbert and Linda Perry Welcome Son Rhodes Emilio | publisher=[[People_(magazine)|People]] | accessdate=2015-03-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170710031626/http://celebritybabies.people.com/2015/03/02/sara-gilbert-linda-perry-welcome-son-rhodes-emilio/ | archive-date=2017-07-10 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/life/people/2015/03/02/sara-gilbert-wife-welcome-baby-boy/24274369/ | title=Sara Gilbert, Linda Perry welcome baby boy | publisher=[[USA_Today|USA Today]] | accessdate=2015-03-02 | author=Oldenburg, Ann}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url= http://www.latimes.com/entertainment/gossip/la-et-mg-sara-gilbert-baby-son-the-talk-linda-perry-20150302-story.html |title= Sara Gilbert, Linda Perry are parents of a new baby boy |work= [[LA_Times|LA Times]] |author= Christie D'Zurilla |date= 2015-03-02 |accessdate= 2017-10-21}}</ref>

吉爾伯特是一位[[素食主义者|素食主义者]]。吉爾伯特有[[猶太|猶太]]血統<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.imdb.com/name/nm0004960/bio | work=IMDb | title=Sara Gilbert - Biography}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.interfaithfamily.com/arts_and_entertainment/popular_culture/interfaith_celebrities_the_talks_hosts_and_david_schwimmers_bride/|title=Interfaith Celebrities: The Talk's Hosts and David Schwimmers Bride|accessdate=June 22, 2018|date=October 26, 2010|last=Bloom|first=Nate|work=InterfaithFamily.com}}</ref>。1997年畢業於耶魯大學。

